HEADWORD: Crapulous
<hw>Crap"u*lous</hw> <pr>(-l?s)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>crapulentus</ets>, <ets>crapulosus</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>crapuleux</ets>.]</ety> <def>Surcharged with liquor; sick from
excessive indulgence in liquor; drunk; given to excesses.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
